metadata.description: Astrohedz is a collection of 10,000 unique Astrohedz NFTs (with four sub-collections from different planets) originating in the Enefty Galaxy (on the Ethereum blockchain). Using a standard ERC-721 smart contract and backed by IPFS, each Astrohedz NFT is your ticket to adventure in our upcoming pay-to-earn topview action/adventure/crafting game and metaverse. Visit www.astrohedz.com for more info.
metadata.name: Astrohedz #1
